query:
-- Buscar tenant Hapvida
SELECT id, name FROM tenants WHERE name LIKE '%Hapvida%';

-- Buscar produto 443060
SELECT id, internalCode, name, tenantId FROM products WHERE internalCode = '443060';

-- Buscar endereço H01-01-01
SELECT id, code, tenantId, zoneId FROM warehouseLocations WHERE code = 'H01-01-01';

-- Buscar estoque do produto 443060 no endereço H01-01-01
SELECT 
  i.productId,
  i.locationId,
  i.tenantId,
  i.quantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as available,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wz.code as zoneCode,
  p.internalCode as productCode
FROM inventory i
INNER JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
INNER JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wl.zoneId = wz.id
INNER JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE p.internalCode = '443060' AND wl.code = 'H01-01-01';
